    {
      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Trim, then chop <strong>half</strong> your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> into batons, then trim and finely slice the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>cornflour</strong> with 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Stir in your<strong> red chilli relish</strong> – this is your <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1653403144938-x200.jpg",
