    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped ginger </strong>(save the rest for later!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
