    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the<strong> cooled rice</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until all of the rice is coated – this is your <strong>fried rice</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>fried rice</strong> to a plate and return the pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
