    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped pepper </strong>and <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> ginger </strong>and cook for 2-3 min until the pepper has started to soften</p><p>Drain, then add your <strong>king</strong> <strong>prawns</strong>,<strong> spring onion batons</strong> and <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until the prawns have cooked through and the sauce is thick and sticky – these are your <strong>sweet chilli king prawns</strong></p>",
